{"parse":{"title":"Lightning Eel","pageid":44846,"wikitext":{"*":"<onlyinclude>{{{{{tpl|tooltip}}}\n|mode={{{mode|}}}\n|arg={{{arg|}}}\n|sell={{cost|||10}}\n|icon=INV_Misc_Fish_12\n|quality=Common\n|itemid=13757\n|ilvl=45\n|name=Lightning Eel}}</onlyinclude>\n\n== Source ==\n'''Lightning Eel''' is obtained by [[fishing]] in the waters around [[Karazhan]] in [[Deadwind Pass]], at [[Frostfire Hot Springs]] in [[Winterspring]], in the [[Thondroril River | river]] that seprates [[Western Plaguelands]] and [[Eastern Plaguelands]], in [[Bloodvenom Falls]] in [[Felwood]], in the [[Verdantis River]] and top of the [[The Twin Colossals]] in [[Feralas]], within [[Zul'Gurub]], in the [[Western Plaguelands]], off the shores of [[Isle of Quel'Danas]], and also found in rivers & [[Lake Elune'ara]] of [[Moonglade]].\n\nUsed as a quest item for [[Craftsman's Writ - Lightning Eel]] to obtain an [[Insignia of the Crusade]] or [[Insignia of the Dawn]] and +75 [[Argent Dawn]] rep.\n\n== Lightning Eel as an Ingredient ==\nLightning Eel is used in the following [[Cooking]] recipe:\n*{{item|icon=|Stormchops}}\n\n== Lightning Eel as a quest objective ==\n*{{questlong|Neutral|60|Craftsman's Writ - Lightning Eel}} (30 required)\n\n==External links==\n<!-- Read http://www.wowwiki.com/WoWWiki:External_links before posting your links here.\nLinks that do not conform to the rules will be DELETED.\nRepeat violations may result in a BAN.\nHave a nice day. :) -->\n{{elinks-item|13757}}\n{{Elink|link=http://www.elsanglin.com/fish/lightning_eel.html |site=El's Extreme Anglin' |icon=elsanglin}}\n[[Category:Eels]]\n[[Category:World of Warcraft common items]]"}}}